{"tid":898890,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺東涌D大陸呀婆好得意","createTime":"2018-11-12T04:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T07:49:55.000Z","uid":132572,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c0d5e4284e526724391f8096934bd075d26eb0","tid":898890,"uid":132572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:09:50.000Z","msg":"見到佢地帶晒D旅行團小黃帽<br />\n天真無邪露埋隻金牙咁哈哈笑<br />\n佢地黎香港既前一晚心情應該好開心又興奮<br />\n同佢地講野無論講廣東話定普通話都淨係識笑住咁 嗯 哦 哈哈<br />\n成隻寵物咁 好似羊咩咩呀 好鬼得意<br />\n諗起之前成日點屌支那 又要劏又要殺<br />\n見到D咁得意既呀婆 心情真係好複雜<br />\n好想去豆下佢地下巴"},{"pid":"4455155419a04907303089b0accf47ec8de56901","tid":898890,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"想俾條撚佢地含"},{"pid":"9502c5ef8062cb3229d82630c2154338bcb5f31b","tid":898890,"uid":57504,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:12:09.000Z","msg":"烚熟咁<br />\n發夢喺海洋公園見過呢啲擋住部電梯，一拳打埋去都喺度笑"},{"pid":"faacd48a1f00f2355986f0401da60d30d1e4f978","tid":898890,"uid":29090,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:19:35.000Z","msg":"仲好chill 咁smoke weed 添<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hbNLW2O.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhbNLW2O.gif&h=43f58178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b7fe3ee7aca28e629172729d4881752f0d5bbc0","tid":898890,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:21:19.000Z","msg":"n年前入南丫島<br />\n個陣啱啱上中學<br />\n12/3歲到<br />\n個陣已經自己週圍行<br />\n屋企行去元朗<br />\n（住九龍）<br />\n跟電車路環頭行去環尾<br />\n去離島蒲<br />\n咁係南丫島蕩失路<br />\n咁咁啱有個阿婆<br />\n睇樣應該水上人黎<br />\n好黑<br />\nok高<br />\n超nice超好笑容<br />\n話我聽點行去邊樹邊樹<br />\n個下真心有少少<br />\n唔識講"},{"pid":"6809b8e2605b062ac9bad5f4cbaba3ca5c0ade05","tid":898890,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4455155419a04907303089b0accf47ec8de56901","tid":898890,"uid":39796,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T04:11:40.000Z","msg":"想俾條撚佢地含"},"citedBy":0,"r